---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Melvin Hogan | Independent UX & AI Consultant: Websites, Apps & Branding"
  description="Independent UX and AI consultant helping you ship websites, apps, and branding with clear strategy, modern craft, and practical use of AI."
  ogTitle="Melvin Hogan | Independent UX & AI Consultant"
  ogDescription="Websites, apps, and branding, grounded in UX practice and practical AI, for teams who want a coherent story and shippable design."
  ogImage="/assets/images/689564b51e5fd0bf98ed6d1a_Opengraph.png"
  twitterTitle="Melvin Hogan | Independent UX & AI Consultant"
  twitterDescription="Websites, apps, and branding, grounded in UX practice and practical AI, for teams who want a coherent story and shippable design."
  current="home"
  wfPageId="5f7f7c04e1b73c803fd0118e"
  bodyClass="body-2"
  linkedinUrl="https://www.linkedin.com/in/melvinhogan/"
>
  <main id="main-content">
    <section
      data-w-id="01da31c1-7d2d-d94a-2d39-9b10f2547fb2"
      style="opacity:0"
      class="sitetitle"
    >
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer w-container">
        <h1 class="main-headline">
          Independent UX & AI consulting for<br />websites, apps & branding
        </h1>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section aria-labelledby="intro-heading">
      <h2 id="intro-heading" class="sr-only">Introduction</h2>
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer w-container">
        <div
          id="w-node-f21b753c-5896-99fa-6c88-1056bdafc721-3fd0118e"
          data-w-id="f21b753c-5896-99fa-6c88-1056bdafc721"
          style="opacity:0"
          class="w-layout-layout quick-stack-9 wf-layout-layout"
        >
          <div class="w-layout-cell">
            <p class="callout">
              I work as an <em>independent UX and AI consultant</em>, partnering directly with founders and teams
              to shape what you ship and how it shows up in the world. That means websites that tell a clear story,
              apps with flows people can follow, and branding that ties the whole experience together.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-layout-cell">
            <p class="callout">
              AI belongs in the workflow where it earns its place: exploring directions faster, drafting and
              structuring content, and pressure-testing ideas before you sink build time. You still get taste,
              judgment, and craft, with less friction between “we should” and “we shipped it.”
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            id="w-node-f13735bc-6bb2-cf9d-a023-f09b167f326e-3fd0118e"
            class="w-layout-cell center"
          >
            <p class="callout point">
              One thread from brand to interface, so your site, your app, and your story feel like the same product.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="bio" aria-labelledby="profile-heading">
      <h2 id="profile-heading" class="sr-only">About Melvin Hogan</h2>
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-13 w-container">
        <img
          src="/assets/images/6827517d26402a8aa52628e8_profilebw.jpeg"
          loading="lazy"
          style="opacity:0"
          data-w-id="1991635a-76e1-e480-ce6a-1e3d5a836bde"
          alt=""
          class="profile"
        />
        <p data-w-id="eebc4aea-0262-4e1d-7463-52b9ffb77c5d" style="opacity:0" class="callout">
          I'm Melvin Hogan, the "M" in the logo above. With 20+ years in UX and product, I focus on website
          creation, app creation, and branding for clients who want a senior partner in the room, not a generic deck.
          Read more about how I work and who I've helped. &nbsp;
        </p>
        <a href="/bio.html" class="contactbutton w-button">About my practice</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section aria-labelledby="services-heading">
      <h2 id="services-heading" class="sr-only">Services</h2>
      <div
        id="w-node-e56b61ca-20c5-0ba4-0f59-ac0fe74b377c-3fd0118e"
        class="w-layout-layout quick-stack-8 wf-layout-layout"
      >
        <div
          data-w-id="e56b61ca-20c5-0ba4-0f59-ac0fe74b377d"
          style="opacity:0"
          class="w-layout-cell features"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/6831129d87ffa38c4469dad4_Brain.svg"
            loading="lazy"
            alt=""
            class="image-37"
          />
          <div class="bullets">
            <h3 class="bullet-heading">Websites & digital presence</h3>
            <p>
              Structure, narrative, and UX so your site converts attention into trust and reflects how you actually
              work.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-w-id="e7515e9a-621f-2ed9-68b2-445afbf47e20"
          style="opacity:0"
          class="w-layout-cell features"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/683115beb7f46d4871032973_Eye.svg"
            loading="lazy"
            alt=""
            class="image-37"
          />
          <div class="bullets">
            <h3 class="bullet-heading">Apps & product UX</h3>
            <p>
              Flows, IA, and interface clarity for web and mobile, so your product feels obvious to the people who
              rely on it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-w-id="49759350-abbe-35c1-c8cc-6cda0ed7a67b"
          style="opacity:0"
          class="w-layout-cell features"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/6831169e6c7c236c76645ec6_Profile.svg"
            loading="lazy"
            alt=""
            class="image-37"
          />
          <div class="bullets">
            <h3 class="bullet-heading">Branding & story</h3>
            <p>
              Voice, visual direction, and consistency across touchpoints, so your brand reads as intentional, not
              improvised.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
      <div id="contact" class="w-layout-blockcontainer w-container">
        <h2 id="contact-heading" class="sr-only">Book a consultation</h2>
        <a
          href="https://app.usemotion.com/meet/mel-hogan/cultureeval"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="contactbutton w-button"
        >
          Book a free 30-minute call
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <section class="hidden">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer hidden w-container">
      <div
        id="w-node-_8ee814aa-884c-0909-41d6-7ad7692ac7cc-3fd0118e"
        class="w-layout-layout quick-stack-6 wf-layout-layout"
      >
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder"><div class="table-heading">Client</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder center"><div class="table-heading">Project</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder right"><div class="table-heading">Learn more</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder"><div>AAMC</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder center"><div>Component Library</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell cell-17 tableborder"><a href="#" class="custombutton w-button">Button Text</a></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder"><div>Jensen Precast</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder center"><div>Dispatch tool</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell cell-16 tableborder"><a href="#" class="custombutton w-button">Button Text</a></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder"><div>C2FO</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell tableborder center"><div>UX Team Design</div></div>
        <div class="w-layout-cell cell-19 tableborder"><a href="#" class="custombutton w-button">Button Text</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="hidden">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer w-container">
      <div class="work-title">AAMC: Finishing the airplane</div>
      <p class="paragraph-7">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse varius enim in eros elementum tristique.
